concept.title: Software domain elements
concept.shortdesc: The elements in the software domain each have a specific semantic purpose.

dlentry.dd:
message phrase
A server log entry of I:O is equivalent to the text message, Information : successful.

message block
The following are the server log entry codes: I:O I:1 P:0 P:1

message number
A server log entry of I:O is equivalent to the text message, Information : successful.

command name
Use the dir command to list the files and folders in the selected directory.

variable (to be provided by user) name
Use the dir/p to pause at the end of each page. You need to press a key to see the rest of the information.

file name or path, or URI
The server log is saved in the log.txt file.

user input
After you type cd.. enter dir at the end of the prompt.
